most of them would probably be enough to bring them back in line with high dmg/mana ratio, and keep them doing damage slower than normal nukers.<br>
<br>
And independant of any other changes, necro DoTs (well ANYBODY's DoTs) should stack between people.  So one necro can't cast their best dot 10 times on a mob, but 10 necros can all cast the same dot on the mob, and they all stick.  There's really no reason why they shouldn't stack as well as any other caster.<br>
<br>
Just clarifying those points.<br>
