<br>
Are druids horrendously broken, no. Do the druids have some issues that need to be looked at, yes. The point of the petition and the rants that followed (DPS, Healing, Group/Raiding desireability) were not to become overpowered as they were Pre-Kunark, but to get some sort of response to a class that has been trickled away since Kunark.<br>
<br>
To adress some of the Magician's concerns I agree the druid spell lins should have been Cold based like the shamans not fire, but you cannot put the genie back in the bottle. I would seriously debate Druid utility vs Mage Utility, but the argument will become moot soon as VI has consistantly been giving our &quot;utility abilities&quot; to everyone on right-click gear with every expansion.<br>
<br>
To sum it all up the consistant ranting has died down now that we are aware that VI is looking the druid community over again, and while not everyone will be happy most of us will be ok wiht the changes.<br>
